00:00:02,720 --> 00:00:08,420
My first errand. Summer adventure special.

2
00:00:12,420 --> 00:00:17,830
In the Seto Inland Sea we find the second biggest island next to Awaji island

3
00:00:17,820 --> 00:00:21,020
the first errand will take place on Shōdo island.

4
00:00:21,020 --> 00:00:27,400
The film "Twenty-four eyes" takes place here.

5
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:34,530
Since they made the film there they've opened up the filmset for tourists to visit.

6
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:38,690
This will be the goal for the first errand.

7
00:00:38,680 --> 00:00:43,760
It's about a young female teacher and 12 first-year students

8
00:00:43,760 --> 00:00:48,040
and how she reaches the hearts of those students.

9
00:00:57,560 --> 00:01:07,260
The teacher would ride her bicycle all the way round the sea shore and through the town to school on the opposite side.

10
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:13,210
