11
00:01:12,500 --> 00:01:20,220
Kairi
3 years old

12
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:17,140
With the 3 year old Kairi who can greet people with a confident voice.

13
00:01:17,140 --> 00:01:22,440
He can also hand customers their voucher.
"He can do the errand if it's in the movie set" is what his dad said.

14
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:25,980
But as expected he can't go by bicycle.

15
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:26,440
He still can't ride one.

16
00:01:26,020 --> 00:01:31,440
Since it takes 30 minutes with the bus how would he get there is what the father worried about.

17
00:01:31,450 --> 00:01:34,520
But they found a clue in the movie.

18
00:01:43,860 --> 00:01:47,350
When the teacher hurt herself she returned to the town by boat.

19
00:01:47,340 --> 00:01:55,720
The exact same route as the teacher sailed is open every spring holiday.

20
00:01:57,380 --> 00:02:00,900
The sailing time is merely 10 minutes.

21
00:02:00,900 --> 00:02:08,240
Kairi's first errand will fall on the second week of April on a Thursday.

22
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:08,240
Wonder if he can do it by himself.

23
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:14,820
And now finally it's that morning. Kairi's mother will ask him to help out with an errand.

24
00:02:14,820 --> 00:02:18,700
