26
00:02:25,730 --> 00:02:31,400
It's not going too well.

27
00:02:25,730 --> 00:02:31,400
Oh, it nice.

28
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:37,160
Next up wipe the table. Yes, that's it.
You are really helpful.

29
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:43,740
