60
00:04:14,020 --> 00:04:19,260
He will then deliver the vouchers to his father waiting in the village.

61
00:04:19,260 --> 00:04:20,130
High five!

62
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:22,130
Is he excited about going now?

63
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,450
High five.

64
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:25,250
Amazing.

65
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:31,460
Maybe not after all.

66
00:04:31,460 --> 00:04:33,140
He stopped.

67
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:38,310
His sister cheered with her support.

68
