119
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:50,550
The boat is leaving.

120
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:53,990
It was requested to go the film set village.

121
00:07:53,980 --> 00:07:58,270
While it takes 10 minutes each way it takes time for the tourists to board.

122
