The harshness of the ocean as well as its kindness the 3 year old man who knows this well...

126
00:08:07,580 --> 00:08:10,110
Kairi!

127
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:10,630
- So cool.
- Cool.

128
00:08:11,740 --> 00:08:15,010
Blue Line!

129
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:18,490
Blue Line!

130
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:26,470
Just like his father wanted. A confident boy who loves the ocean and its ships.

131
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:30,330
Shōdo island where both the ocean and the mountains are near

132
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:36,430
