00:08:49,940 --> 00:08:55,370
No matter how loud his singing is
it bothers no one.

138
00:08:58,860 --> 00:09:00,650
Is it coming?

139
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:03,550
It's coming. It's coming.

140
00:09:03,540 --> 00:09:05,330
The boat is coming back.

141
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:07,430
Welcome back.

142
00:09:07,420 --> 00:09:13,190
Yahoo!
It came, it came!

143
00:09:09,260 --> 00:09:11,770
- What an energetic kid.
- He's great.

144
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:17,570
Hello.

145
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:19,030
Amazing kid.

146
00:09:17,580 --> 00:09:21,450
Yes, just as he has been asked to.
Greeting people with a confident voice.

147
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:24,050
The usual fare is 500 yen.

148
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:31,370
