149
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:34,330
I wish to go to Benten Circle.

150
00:09:33,980 --> 00:09:35,630
Ah, he said it.

151
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,630
What?

152
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:38,570
To Benten Circle, please.

153
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:38,570
Yes, I understand.

154
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:41,370
I came to deliver something.

155
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:41,370
I understand.

156
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,930
He was able to say it.

157
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:47,830
