158
00:09:47,540 --> 00:09:49,150
How lucky.

159
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:51,170
Bye bye.

160
00:09:57,820 --> 00:10:01,530
The weather is so fine today and there's no wind.

161
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:07,570
