162
00:10:07,300 --> 00:10:09,910
What an amazing view.

163
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:14,310
- What a nice expression.
- That's the best.

164
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:24,150
Within 10 minutes and they can finally see the film set village.

165
00:10:24,540 --> 00:10:26,470
Carry me please.

166
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:31,370
