191
00:11:55,770 --> 00:12:00,650
Erika and Minami who always give
him candy are right there.

192
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:03,310
Not here. He's not here.

193
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:05,030
Isn't he going to go in?

194
00:12:05,020 --> 00:12:08,870
He wasn't there. I will go over there and see.

195
00:12:08,860 --> 00:12:10,870
