225
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:55,810
He can finally hear Kairi's voice.

226
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:57,030
Finally.

227
00:13:57,020 --> 00:13:59,860
I came here for a delivery.

228
00:13:59,930 --> 00:14:02,970
