I feel so proud.

246
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:48,370
I feel so proud.

247
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:50,740
Yeah, the world of movies.

248
00:14:50,730 --> 00:14:52,090
That's why I felt proud.

249
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:56,630
